     // Floor input: data-testid="clip-floor-input"
     ```

   - **`/packages/web/src/workspace/Viewport3DLayersPanel.test.tsx`** (CREATED)
     - Tests: renders panel, checkbox checked state, toggle dispatch, clip elevation inputs, null on clear, blur callbacks, viewpoint hint display/hide
     - Uses `makeProps()` factory function with `vi.fn()` mocks

   - **`/packages/web/src/workspace/RedesignedWorkspace.tsx`** (MODIFIED)
     - Added import: `import { Viewport3DLayersPanel, VIEWER_HIDDEN_KIND_KEYS } from './Viewport3DLayersPanel'`
     - Added store subscriptions (lines ~125-133):
       ```tsx
       const viewerCategoryHidden = useBimStore((s) => s.viewerCategoryHidden);
       const toggleViewerCategoryHidden = useBimStore((s) => s.toggleViewerCategoryHidden);
       const viewerClipElevMm = useBimStore((s) => s.viewerClipElevMm);
