   - **`RedesignedWorkspace.tsx` line 1108 - `SectionModeShell` passing `activeLevelLabel`**: After I changed the component interface, the calling code in `CanvasMount` still used `elementsById`. Attempted fix by passing `activeLevelLabel` but this got reverted by linter. Currently the component has `elementsById` and `RedesignedWorkspace.tsx` passes `elementsById`, so this is consistent.

